<Layout title="Formation">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/info.css" slot="style"/>
    <main>
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
            <Card
                href="/"
                title="Back"
                body="Keep exploring"
            />
			<Card
				href="/competencies/"
				title="Competencies"
				body="Here you can find my main techical strenghts and focuses. Be my guest!"
			/>
            <Card
                href="/experiences/"
                title="Work History"
                body="Find out which business I collaborated with and in which fashion"
            />
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <ol>
                <h3><strong>Computer Science And Engineering Course </strong><span class="subtitle">with no degree</span><br>
                    <span class="subtitle">at University of Pisa, Pisa, Italy ()</span>
                </h3>
                <ul>
                    <p>During the course I:</p>
                    <ol>learned to code in the following languages: JavaScript, MySQL and C++</ol>
                    <ol>learned to use the following languages: HTML e CSS</ol>
                    <ol>learned the conceptual, logic and physical design of a database as well as the core concepts (queries, mutations, triggers, stored procedures and views)</ol>
