                    <span class="subtitle">at Formatica S.c.a.r.l. Pisa, Italy ()</span>
                </h3>
                <ul>
                    <p>During the course I learned/practiced:</p>
                    <ol>the following programming languages: Bash, Java</ol>
                    <ol>The following tools: Docker, GitLab as a tool for the CI/CD, Wireshark, Packet Tracer</ol>
                    <ol>The use of the OpenSSL library for the creation of certificates and private/public keys</ol>
                </ul>
            </ol>
        </ul>
    </main>
</Layout>